plot: Supergirl fights against her aunt and learns some heartbreaking news about her mom, while Catco is dealing with a hacker.

Kara must face her evil aunt Astra when she threatens the safety of National City and challenges Kara's beliefs about her mother while Cat must also face her own problems when she is threatened to be removed from her job as CEO of CatCo when a few personal e-mails are exposed by a hacker that could damage her career.—Amelia
